  69:../Middlewares/stedgeai-lib/Npu/ll_aton/ll_sw_integer.c ****   1. reshape of the weights from weights tensor -> weights_perm tensor
  70:../Middlewares/stedgeai-lib/Npu/ll_aton/ll_sw_integer.c ****   2. map the matmul operation on the library dense_forward function.
  71:../Middlewares/stedgeai-lib/Npu/ll_aton/ll_sw_integer.c ****           this requires 1d input (on ch) and 2d weights (ch e chin). in particular:
  72:../Middlewares/stedgeai-lib/Npu/ll_aton/ll_sw_integer.c ****           - input: 1,1,NIN,1
  73:../Middlewares/stedgeai-lib/Npu/ll_aton/ll_sw_integer.c ****           - weights already permuted: 1,1,NOUT,NIN
