  75:../Middlewares/stedgeai-lib/Npu/ll_aton/ll_sw_integer.c ****           - scratch 1,1,NIN*2+NOUT*10
  76:../Middlewares/stedgeai-lib/Npu/ll_aton/ll_sw_integer.c ****           - output 1,1,NOUT,1
  77:../Middlewares/stedgeai-lib/Npu/ll_aton/ll_sw_integer.c ****   */
